    "synopsis": "The Soul Drinkers have been taken alive by the Imperial Fists and brought aboard the Phalanx — the planetoid-fortress of Dorn's gene-sons — to stand trial for their crimes against the Imperium. Sarpedon defends his chapter before an audience of Astartes, Inquisitors, and Mechanicus, until a confession leads to a vault on Selaaca and Daenyathos is brought back to face trial beside the warriors he engineered. The series finale closes the chapter-tragedy at bittersweet cost.",
